{"word":"ὑπεργάζομαι","slug":"ὑπεργάζομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὑπεργάζομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>άσομαι</el>) </el><p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to work under, plough up, prepare</i> for sowing, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to subdue, reduce</i>: <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> in <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> sense, <i>to be subdued</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><i>to do underhand</i> or <i>secretly</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>IV. </b>= <a href='S:ὑπηρετέω'><el>ὑπηρετέω</el></a>, <i>to do a service</i>: <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> in <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> sense, <el>πόλλ' ὑπείργασται φίλα</el> many kind acts <i>have been done</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}